rasts(cancer - normal)` + `eBayes`) to compute the top 250\nDE probes (`topTable(..., adjust='fdr', number=250)`) and save to\n`output/deg_results.csv` via `write.csv(...)`. Do NOT produce a volcano plot.\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- At least `output/deg_results.csv` must exist when you submit.\n- Full output set expected: deg_results.csv under `output/`.\n\nWhen the deliverables are in `output/`, call `submit_done(success=true)` with a short\nsummary of how you solved it.\n\n## Workspace (read-only summary)\n```json\n{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"exprs.csv\": {\n      \"_file\": \"exprs.csv\"\n    },\n    \"meta.csv\": {\n      \"_file\": \"meta.csv\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/deg_results.csv` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_CjrOHzLtKt1menHnqZq4bi2D", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Load the necessary libraries, specifically the limma package.\\n2. Read the expression data from 'input/exprs.csv' and the metadata from 'input/meta.csv'.\\n3. Create a design matrix using the group column from the metadata.\\n4. Fit a linear model to the expression data using the lmFit function.\\n5. Define the contrast of interest (cancer vs normal) using the makeContrasts function.\\n6. Apply the contrast to the fitted model using the contrasts.fit function.\\n7. Compute empirical Bayes statistics using the eBayes function.\\n8. Extract the top 250 differentially expressed probes using the topTable function with FDR adjustment.\\n9. Write the results to 'output/deg_results.csv'.\\n10. Verify the output file exists and submit the task as complete.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (744 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_CjrOHzLtKt1menHnqZq4bi2D"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_UZnxy7wmtjDJyvB7mpmYcYkM", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"code\": \"library(limma)\"}", "name": "run_rscript"}}, {"id": "call_eA3ibOhpbVhN26ZYv0in5omq", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"relative_path\": \"input/exprs.csv\"}", "name": "read_text_file"}}, {"id": "call_b2njqdlwgK0jNjuku6tQSZP1", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"relative_path\": \"input/meta.csv\"}", "name": "read_text_file"}}]}], "hide_old_env_states": false, "hide_old_action_content": false}, "observation": [{"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (744 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_CjrOHzLtKt1menHnqZq4bi2D"}], "next_observation": [{"role": "tool", "content": "exit=0\nstdout:\n\nstderr:\n", "name": "run_rscript", "tool_call_id": "call_UZnxy7wmtjDJyvB7mpmYcYkM"}, {"role": "tool", "content": ",GSM0001,GSM0002,GSM0003,GSM0004,GSM0005,GSM0006,GSM0007,GSM0008\nPROBE_00000,10.4568,10.4481,10.4666,10.7106,7.9617,7.5508,8.0997,7.9198\nPROBE_00001,7.9349,8.0348,8.0697,8.3491,8.1970,8.0332,7.7785,7.6956\nPROBE_00002,8.0739,8.3933,8.0125,7.9681,8.1595,7.5639,7.9063,8.1471\nPROBE_00003,8.2620,7.9278,8.1130,8.0745,8.2347,7.6660,8.1705,7.5456\nPROBE_00004,7.2140,7.8179,7.7253,8.2628,8.1993,7.6343,8.2542,7.6993\nPROBE_00005,7.9741,7.9118,8.0343,8.2456,8.1915,8.1050,8.1950,8.1435\nPROBE_00006,7.8119,7.7848,7.8590,8.1498,7.9250,8.7007,7.7542,7.6703\nPROBE_00007,8.2305,8.4266,8.1517,8.2507,8.4279,7.9718,7.5731,7.8404\nPROBE_00008,8.2859,7.5669,8.0101,8.0760,7.9053,8.2171,8.1742,8.6964\nPROBE_00009,8.1860,7.8172,7.8315,7.7505,8.2857,7.8300,7.9789,8.2248\nPROBE_00010,7.7830,7.9119,7.4476,7.6753,7.8297,8.1247,8.3580,7.9945\nPROBE_00011,8.0784,8.0504,8.3254,8.2680,8.0821,7.6967,8.2710,8.1143\nPROBE_00012,8.3681,7.9910,8.5859,7.8923,8.4779,8.0345,7.8451,7.6615\nPROBE_00013,7.9547,8.4270,8.2449,8.2067,7.2872,8.2133